@startuml
title Command

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: Encapsulate a request as an object; support queuing, logging, undo.

**Use when**: Decouple invoker from receiver; macro/undo operations.

**Key participants**: Command, ConcreteCommand, Receiver, Invoker.
endlegend

interface Command {
  +execute()
}

class ConcreteCommand
class Receiver {
  +action()
}

class Invoker {
  -cmd : Command
  +setCommand(c: Command)
  +invoke()
}

Command <|.. ConcreteCommand
ConcreteCommand o-- Receiver
Invoker o-- Command
@enduml